    {
        "id": 373,
        "slug": "dental-care",
        "title": "Dental Care",
        "url": "https://cmcenters.org/health-services/dental-care/",
        "date": "2023-07-18 04:15:52",
        "modified": "2025-05-07 09:26:23",
        "excerpt": "",
        "content": "<ul>\r\n \t<li>Dental exams and with oral cancer screening</li>\r\n \t<li>Regular and deep cleanings</li>\r\n \t<li>Fillings</li>\r\n \t<li>Fluoride treatments</li>\r\n \t<li>Dentures</li>\r\n \t<li>Crowns and bridges</li>\r\n \t<li>Root canals</li>\r\n \t<li>Oral surgery including extractions</li>\r\n \t<li>Space maintainers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDental care is an important part of your whole health, which is why it’s important to see your dentist regularly.\r\n\r\nWe understand that dental visits can be a source of anxiety for many people. That’s why our caring, professional dentistry team ensures you feel as comfortable as possible every time you visit–even if it has been a long time since you last saw a dentist.",
