        "excerpt": "",
        "content": "<ul>\r\n \t<li>Wellness and prevention classes</li>\r\n \t<li>Managing diabetes, asthma, hypertension</li>\r\n \t<li>Reproductive health education</li>\r\n \t<li>Online classes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKnowledge is power. Especially when it comes to your health. That’s why we give you the resources you need to make informed decisions about your health, and the health of your entire family.\r\n\r\nFrom preventing and managing chronic health issues to understanding your options when it comes to reproductive health, CMC has the information, guidance, and support you need to live your healthiest life.",
