    {
        "id": 1953,
        "slug": "recovery",
        "title": "Recovery / SUD Services",
        "url": "https://cmcenters.org/health-services/recovery/",
        "date": "2024-02-24 18:02:42",
        "modified": "2026-02-11 14:08:55",
        "excerpt": "",
        "content": "<ul>\r\n \t<li>Full assessment for care needs</li>\r\n \t<li>Medication-Assisted Treatment (MAT)</li>\r\n \t<li>Individual &amp; group counseling</li>\r\n \t<li>Case management</li>\r\n \t<li>Housing assistance</li>\r\n \t<li>Transportation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 2.5rem;\"><strong>Help is available for individuals experiencing substance use disorder (SUD).</strong></p>\r\nIf you or someone you care about is seeking treatment for SUD, we offer resources and support to help navigate the recovery process. Our specialists provide personalized, evidence-based care and work with each patient to identify the treatment options that best meet their needs.\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;\">Outpatient Care</p>\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+12099405662\">(209) 940-5662</a>\r\n1031 Waterloo Rd, Stockton CA 95205\r\n200 Cottage Ave #104, Manteca CA 95336\r\n730 N. Central Ave, Tracy CA 95376\r\n201 N. Stanislaus St #101, Stockton CA 95202\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;\">Residential Treatment</p>\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+12097625000\">(209) 762-5000</a>\r\n201 N. Stanislaus St #102, Stockton CA 95202\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;\">Learn more</p>\r\nStay informed about events, programs, and updates! Follow CMCenters on social media or subscribe to our e-news below.\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><a class=\"row-title\" href=\"https://cmcenters.org/cmc-respite-center-journaling-with-tuleburg-press/\" aria-label=\"“CMC Respite Center and Tuleburg Press partner to help patients heal through journaling” (Edit)\">CMC Respite Center and Tuleburg Press partner to help patients heal through journaling</a></li>\r\n \t<li><a class=\"row-title\" href=\"https://cmcenters.org/open-house-to-introduce-manteca-recovery-center/\" aria-label=\"“Open House to Introduce Manteca Recovery Center” (Edit)\">Open House to Introduce Manteca Recovery Center</a></li>\r\n \t<li><a class=\"row-title\" href=\"https://cmcenters.org/growing-youth-program-tackles-behavioral-health-and-sud-challenges/\" aria-label=\"“Growing youth program tackles behavioral-health and SUD challenges” (Edit)\">Growing youth program tackles behavioral-health and SUD challenges</a></li>\r\n</ul>",
        "thumbnail": "/img/2024__02__iStock-1317442790-scaled.jpg",
        "meta": {
            "_edit_last": "10",
            "_edit_lock": "1770847630:10",
            "ignyte_locations[]": {
