    {
        "id": 377,
        "slug": "women-infant-and-children-program-wic",
        "title": "Women, Infants and Children Program (WIC)",
        "url": "https://cmcenters.org/health-services/women-infant-and-children-program-wic/",
        "date": "2023-07-18 04:19:01",
        "modified": "2024-12-10 19:57:19",
        "excerpt": "",
        "content": "WIC is a special supplemental nutrition program for women, infants, and children. WIC helps families get healthy food and a lot more!\r\n\r\nWIC is available at the centers listed at right and at these CMC WIC locations:\r\n<strong>Lodi WIC</strong> 2401 W. Turner Rd #470, Lodi CA 95242 | <a href=\"tel:+2093701750\">(209) 370-1750</a>\r\n<strong>Stockton</strong> WIC 425 N. California St #7, Stockton CA 95202 | <a href=\"tel:209870500\">(209) 870-5000</a>\r\n<strong>Tracy</strong> WIC 73 E. 10th St, Tracy CA 95376 | <a href=\"tel:+2092297800\">(209) 229-7800</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information about the program or to apply, please visit the <a href=\"https://www.cmcwic.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CMC WIC website</a>.",
