    {
        "id": 369,
        "slug": "womens-health",
        "title": "Women's Health",
        "url": "https://cmcenters.org/health-services/womens-health/",
        "date": "2023-07-18 04:13:27",
        "modified": "2026-01-30 14:38:42",
        "excerpt": "",
        "content": "<ul><li>Routine physicals, including cervical cancer screenings\r\n</li><li>Breast exams and referrals for mammograms\r\n</li><li>Free pregnancy testing\r\n</li><li>Prenatal care, postpartum care, and case management\r\n</li><li>Family planning and birth control</li>\r\n<li>STD testing, treatment, and protection</li>\r\n<li>Online classes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>When it comes to reproductive health, CMC is a trusted resource for all of life’s stages. From routine physicals to mammograms to pregnancy testing, we’re here for you.</p>\r\n<p>And when you’re ready to start a family, your reproductive health team is ready, too, with the care and resources you’ll need for a healthy pregnancy.</p>\r\n<p>From prenatal care to postpartum care to case management and beyond, we’re your healthcare partner for life.</p>",
        "thumbnail": "/img/2023__11__CMC-Services-Womens-Health.jpg",
